org.apache.oodt.cas.metadata

Interface MetExtractor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMetExtractor, CmdLineMetExtractor, CopyAndRewriteExtractor, DataSourceMetExtractor, ExternMetExtractor, FilenameTokenMetExtractor, MetReaderExtractor, ParentKeyDataSourceMetExtractor, ProdTypePatternMetExtractor, TikaCmdLineMetExtractor

    public interface MetExtractor
    Version:
    $Revision$

    An interface for Metadata extraction. This interface expects the definition of the following two parameters:

    • file - the file to extract Metadata from.
    • config file - a pointer to the config file for this MetExtractor

    Author:
    mattmann
